<p>A lovely brass incense burner ideal to use with incense cones, Dhoop logs or for the charcoal discs used to burn resin incense. The lid and base both have patterned holes to let the aroma and smoke escape. The burner can be hung in a room or the chain is easy to detach and use as table top burner. Dimensions- 26cm when hung &amp; actual burner is 10cm tall.</p>